{# ====================================================================
   第 2 层: 全局性提示词 — 用户画像上下文
   
   管理员指南：
   - 此模版将用户的全局设置注入到所有 AI 功能中
   - 变量由系统自动从用户画像中读取填充
   - 修改此文件可调整用户画像如何影响 AI 行为
   
   可用变量：
   - user_exam_type: 备考目标 (cet4/cet6/ielts/toefl/gre/kaoyan/bar_exam)
   - user_subject_field: 学科领域 (law/finance/cs/medicine/engineering/humanities...)
   - user_specialty: 细分专业方向
   - user_interest_tags: 兴趣标签列表
   - user_eng_level: 英语水平 (cet4/cet6/ielts5/ielts7/native)
   ==================================================================== #}
{% if user_subject_field or user_specialty or user_exam_type or user_interest_tags %}
## User Academic Profile

{% if user_subject_field %}
- **Subject Field**: {{ user_subject_field }}
{% endif %}
{% if user_specialty %}
- **Specialty Focus**: {{ user_specialty }}
{% endif %}
{% if user_exam_type %}
- **Exam Target**: {{ user_exam_type }}
{% endif %}
{% if user_eng_level %}
- **English Level**: {{ user_eng_level }}
{% endif %}
{% if user_interest_tags %}
- **Interest Areas**: {{ user_interest_tags | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}

**Profile-Driven Instructions**:
{% if user_subject_field or user_specialty %}
- Tailor all content, examples, terminology, and case studies to the user's academic specialty above.
- When selecting vocabulary, prioritize words commonly encountered in {{ user_subject_field | default('academic') }} literature.
- Use domain-relevant contexts and real-world examples from {{ user_specialty | default(user_subject_field) | default('the user\'s field') }}.
{% endif %}
{% if user_exam_type %}
- For vocabulary selection, prioritize words within the scope of the "{{ user_exam_type }}" exam word list.
- Adjust difficulty and format to align with {{ user_exam_type }} exam requirements.
{% endif %}
{% if user_eng_level == 'cet4' %}
- Target language difficulty: CEFR A2-B1, simple sentence structures, high-frequency vocabulary.
{% elif user_eng_level == 'cet6' %}
- Target language difficulty: CEFR B1-B2, moderately complex structures, academic vocabulary.
{% elif user_eng_level == 'ielts5' or user_eng_level == 'ielts7' %}
- Target language difficulty: CEFR B2-C1, sophisticated academic prose with complex clause structures.
{% elif user_eng_level == 'native' %}
- Target language difficulty: CEFR C1-C2, native-level academic prose with discipline-specific register.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
